sequenceDiagram
    participant CS as Charging Station (OCTT)
    participant CSMS as Charging Station Management System

    Note over CS,CSMS: TC_E_19 - Stop transaction options - ParkingBayUnoccupied
    Note over CS,CSMS: Use case: E06(S1) | Requirement: E06.FR.01
    Note over CS,CSMS: Before: Reusable State EVDisconnected (without ending transaction)

    Note over CS,CSMS: [EVDisconnected state - Updated, not Ended, since TxStopPoint=ParkingBayOccupancy]
    CS->>CSMS: StatusNotificationRequest [connectorStatus=Available]
    CSMS-->>CS: StatusNotificationResponse
    CS->>CSMS: NotifyEventRequest [trigger=Delta, actualValue=Available, component.name=Connector, variable.name=AvailabilityState]
    CSMS-->>CS: NotifyEventResponse
    CS->>CSMS: TransactionEventRequest [eventType=Updated, triggerReason=EVCommunicationLost, chargingState=Idle]
    CSMS-->>CS: TransactionEventResponse

    Note over CS,CSMS: [Main test step - ParkingBay departure ends transaction]
    CS->>CSMS: TransactionEventRequest [eventType=Ended, triggerReason=EVDeparted, stoppedReason=Local]
    CSMS-->>CS: TransactionEventResponse
